WITH first_query AS (
  -- First query here
  SELECT module_type, COUNT(master_data)+COUNT(configuration)+COUNT(training)+ 
       SUM(CASE WHEN master_data IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) +
       SUM(CASE WHEN configuration IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) +
       SUM(CASE WHEN training IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS total_count
  FROM "dashboard"."software"
  GROUP BY module_type
),
second_query AS (
  -- Second query here
  SELECT module_type, SUM(total_count) AS overall_count
  FROM(
    SELECT m.module_type, COALESCE(s.total_count, 0) AS total_count
    FROM (
      SELECT DISTINCT module_type
      FROM "dashboard"."software"
    ) AS m
    LEFT JOIN (
      SELECT module_type, COUNT(master_data) AS total_count
      FROM "dashboard"."software"
      WHERE master_data = 'yes'
      GROUP BY module_type
    ) AS s ON m.module_type = s.module_type

    UNION ALL

    SELECT m.module_type, COALESCE(s.total_count, 0) AS total_count
    FROM (
      SELECT DISTINCT module_type
      FROM "dashboard"."software"
    ) AS m
    LEFT JOIN (
      SELECT module_type, COUNT(configuration) AS total_count
      FROM "dashboard"."software"
      WHERE configuration = 'yes'
      GROUP BY module_type
    ) AS s ON m.module_type = s.module_type

    UNION ALL

    SELECT m.module_type, COALESCE(s.total_count, 0) AS total_count
    FROM (
      SELECT DISTINCT module_type
      FROM "dashboard"."software"
    ) AS m
    LEFT JOIN (
      SELECT module_type, COUNT(training) AS total_count
      FROM "dashboard"."software"
      WHERE training = 'yes'
      GROUP BY module_type
    ) AS s ON m.module_type = s.module_type
  )
  AS combined_result
  GROUP BY module_type
)
SELECT f.module_type, (s.overall_count / f.total_count)*100 AS division_result
FROM first_query f
JOIN second_query s ON f.module_type = s.module_type
ORDER BY f.module_type ASC;
